members are stylish.

00:06:51.327 --> 00:06:52.746 position:50% align:center
Guess that's Geika.

00:06:52.829 --> 00:06:54.164 position:50% align:center
Well, Mom, maybe we both

00:06:54.247 --> 00:06:56.291 position:50% align:center
