relaxed than you are now!

00:07:20.690 --> 00:07:22.442 position:50% align:center
[IKUTO groans]

00:07:22.525 --> 00:07:25.153 position:50% align:center
[IKUTO]
My stomach hurts.

00:07:25.236 --> 00:07:28.448 position:50% align:center
I'm so nervous!

00:07:28.531 --> 00:07:31.743 position:50% align:center
[music plays]

00:07:43.755 --> 00:07:50.095 position:50% align:center
[music plays]

00:07:52.180 --> 00:07:55.058 position:50% align:center
[IKUTO] I better get
back for the final check.

00:07:58.228 --> 00:07:59.979 position:50% align:center
[KAORU] Number seven!
The double woven obi

00:08:00.063 --> 00:08:01.981 position:50% align:center
and the accessories
are all out of balance.

00:08:02.065 --> 00:08:03.400 position:50% align:center
Adjust them! Make it work!

00:08:03.483 --> 00:08:05.026 position:50% align:center
Hey, did you find
that silk thread?

00:08:05.110 --> 00:08:07.195 position:50% align:center
[STAFF C] We just ran out.
Let's use a safety pin to--

00:08:07.278 --> 00:08:09.823 position:50% align:center
