00:08:28.842 --> 00:08:30.927 position:50% align:center
Is Toh Ayano the most
noteworthy designer here?

00:08:31.011 --> 00:08:32.470 position:50% align:center
Yeah, he might be.

00:08:32.554 --> 00:08:35.056 position:50% align:center
