I can do it.

00:09:34.532 --> 00:09:36.076 position:50% align:center
[KAORU gasps]

00:09:40.163 --> 00:09:41.623 position:50% align:center
[KAORU] The original
design of that dress

00:09:41.706 --> 00:09:45.251 position:50% align:center
was much more elegant and
delicate than it was in the end.

00:09:45.335 --> 00:09:47.879 position:50% align:center
