into something else.

00:09:50.674 --> 00:09:54.010 position:50% align:center
All because, when
the moment came...

00:09:54.094 --> 00:09:56.388 position:50% align:center
...I didn't raise my hand.

00:09:57.806 --> 00:10:00.725 position:50% align:center
[KAORU] Why do I despise
Ikuto Tsumura so much?

00:10:00.809 --> 00:10:03.687 position:50% align:center
Is it because he ruined
Mr. Hajime's show?

00:10:03.770 --> 00:10:05.105 position:50% align:center
No.

00:10:05.188 --> 00:10:08.066 position:50% align:center
Because he completely ditched
Mr. Hajime's concept?

00:10:08.149 --> 00:10:09.359 position:50% align:center
No.

00:10:09.442 --> 00:10:10.485 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:10:10.568 --> 00:10:12.070 position:50% align:center
[CROWD clapping]

00:10:12.153 --> 00:10:17.283 position:50% align:center
[KAORU] It was that moment when
I heard the audience's applause.

00:10:17.367 --> 00:10:20.495 position:50% align:center
I was absolutely
swept away by it.

00:10:21.955 --> 00:10:23.790 position:50% align:center
Last one!

00:10:23.873 --> 00:10:25.000 position:50% align:center
Go!

00:10:26.251 --> 00:10:28.670 position:50% align:center
