I felt like I'd been beaten.

00:10:28.753 --> 00:10:32.340 position:50% align:center
So... why do I
despise Ikuto Tsumura?

00:10:32.424 --> 00:10:33.633 position:50% align:center
Well...

00:10:33.717 --> 00:10:36.636 position:50% align:center
