of the billowing skirt

00:10:54.696 --> 00:10:58.908 position:50% align:center
to achieve a nice balance
between kimono and modern dress.

00:11:01.244 --> 00:11:03.538 position:50% align:center
[KINU] It really is
a beautiful silhouette.

00:11:03.621 --> 00:11:05.498 position:50% align:center
Better be certain to
offer up some praise,

00:11:05.582 --> 00:11:09.085 position:50% align:center
