back to bite me.

00:11:09.169 --> 00:11:10.670 position:50% align:center
[TAKAOKA]
My goodness.

00:11:10.754 --> 00:11:14.007 position:50% align:center
Using an unforgiving material
like leather to make a kimono?

00:11:14.090 --> 00:11:15.175 position:50% align:center
The knowledge and technique

00:11:15.258 --> 00:11:17.135 position:50% align:center
