achieve this look.

00:11:17.218 --> 00:11:19.471 position:50% align:center
It's all so impressive, Kaoru!

00:11:19.554 --> 00:11:23.516 position:50% align:center
I need that dress. It's perfect
for the Cannes Festival!

00:11:25.602 --> 00:11:28.730 position:50% align:center
