raising your arms.

00:12:04.599 --> 00:12:06.810 position:50% align:center
Sure thing. It's good.

00:12:06.893 --> 00:12:09.104 position:50% align:center
Kanami, how much time?

00:12:09.187 --> 00:12:11.439 position:50% align:center
