00:12:11.523 --> 00:12:14.776 position:50% align:center
Okay. Hmm...

00:12:15.902 --> 00:12:18.196 position:50% align:center
[TAKAOKA] Ooh! It's
finally time for us to see

00:12:18.279 --> 00:12:20.281 position:50% align:center
