00:12:57.819 --> 00:12:59.988 position:50% align:center
Smile.

00:13:00.071 --> 00:13:02.991 position:50% align:center
Well, this is it, you guys!

00:13:03.074 --> 00:13:05.618 position:50% align:center
[STAFF]
We can do it!

00:13:05.702 --> 00:13:07.162 position:50% align:center
[IKUTO]
I'm gonna love this.

00:13:07.245 --> 00:13:08.955 position:50% align:center
Getting to share my collection--

00:13:09.039 --> 00:13:10.123 position:50% align:center
my passion!

00:13:10.206 --> 00:13:12.125 position:50% align:center
All right, here we go!

00:13:12.208 --> 00:13:14.169 position:50% align:center
It's show time!

00:13:15.962 --> 00:13:17.797 position:50% align:center
[IKUTO]
<i>Smile Down the Runway</i> .

